Template: retriever/floppy/packages/progress
Type: text
_Description: Scanning the floppy

Template: retriever/floppy/device
Type: select
_Choices: Cancel, ${DEVS}
_Description: Select your floppy device:
 No standard floppy drive was found. If you have a USB floppy drive or
 some other unusual type of floppy drive, select it from the list. Note
 that the list may also include drives that are not floppy drives. The
 installer will only try to read from the selected device.

Template: retriever/floppy/error
Type: boolean
Default: true
_Description: Cannot read floppy, or not a driver floppy. Retry?
 There was a problem reading data from the floppy disk. Please make sure
 that the right floppy is in the drive. If you continue to have trouble,
 you may have a bad floppy disk.
